    "description": "<div style='text-align:Left;'><div><div><p><span>The current version supersedes the </span><a target='_blank' href='https://doi.org/10.7916/qy18-hj66' rel='nofollow ugc noopener noreferrer'><span><u>GRID3 COD - Health Zones v7.0</u></span></a><span>. The following changes were made:</span></p><ul><li><span>Added data for the provinces of Bas-Uele, Haut-Uele, Kwango, and Nord-Kivu.</span></li><li><span>The data for Tanganyika was updated.</span></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span>Download province level data:</span></p><ul><li><a target='_blank' href='https://academiccommons.columbia.edu/doi/10.7916/768w-1t22/download' rel='nofollow ugc noopener noreferrer'><span>Bas-Uele</span></a></li><li><a target='_blank' href='https://academiccommons.columbia.edu/doi/10.7916/me75-r528/download' rel='nofollow ugc noopener noreferrer'><span>Equateur</span></a></li><li><a target='_blank' href='https://academiccommons.columbia.edu/doi/10.7916/nt5p-3x64/download' rel='nofollow ugc noopener noreferrer'><span>Haut-Katanga</span></a></li><li><a target='_blank' href='https://academiccommons.columbia.edu/doi/10.7916/xh8a-a534/download' rel='nofollow ugc noopener noreferrer'><span>Haut-Lomami</span></a></li><li><a target='_blank' href='https://academiccommons.columbia.edu/doi/10.7916/m8c8-8m53/download' rel='nofollow ugc noopener noreferrer'><span>Haut-Uele</span></a></li><li><a target='_blank' href='https://academiccommons.columbia.edu/doi/10.7916/e4a5-q639/download' rel='nofollow ugc noopener noreferrer'><span>Ituri</span></a></li><li><a target='_blank' href='https://academiccommons.columbia.edu/doi/10.7916/ta5m-r717/download' rel='nofollow ugc noopener noreferrer'><span>Kasa\u00ef</span></a></li><li><a target='_blank' href='https://academiccommons.columbia.edu/doi/10.7916/4xn3-fc33/download' rel='nofollow ugc noopener noreferrer'><span>Kasa\u00ef-Central</span></a></li><li><a target='_blank' href='https://academiccommons.columbia.edu/doi/10.7916/f1x2-mg26/download' rel='